9T05:11:59.000Z","msg":"sony white balance=垃圾"},{"pid":"39b9d867978c152f31b93f5137961cbdf944949a","tid":45384,"uid":67094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:21:23.000Z","msg":"有冇圖睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c30f1dfcb674d48555798fcc0c2dfeb45b20efb","tid":45384,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:22:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>色階我指既唔係色調<br />\n我指既係色彩過渡變化<br />\n<br />\n例如肉色去黑色RX100 可能過2000 種色咁，D750 係7-8000種左右</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係因為sensor大細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定唔同廠所以先咁</blockquote><br />\ncolor depth問題,sensor大d通常bit數都多D"},{"pid":"f85dbcd36ecd90e6d2130ec3d5eb02f0a6eab10e","tid":45384,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:22:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大部分同意 Sony d色睇下真係怪怪地<br />\n同埋室內影人都係大機有保證d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\njpg 用住先就vivid -1 -1 +1<br />\nraw 就去mobile01 拎LR 改色調檔、上M9 AS<br />\n然後再用VSCO PRESET</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無知一問 點解要拎改色調檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSony本身無論jpg raw 影人都偏黃<br />\nm4開始有改善，m5紅色表現又再好一啲<br />\n但低光時效果仲係唔係好掂<br />\n<br />\n所以有啲人就抄咗其他機既調色、基本上一韃落去就可以換到，當然畫質係會有輕微既損失<br />\n<br />\n但至少你唔駛用個lightroom 調到屌那媽<br />\n當然有啲懶撚直接掟個VSCO PRESET就算"},{"pid":"737f6094189653875102e91faddcfcb12fb74632","tid":45384,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:24:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>sony white balance=垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話事話，LR adjust white balance無Apple 個aperture咁准<br />\n平時aperture adjust white balance點落人塊面道就出到正確顏色<br />\nLR個WB一點落去成張相藍左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1bfa9d76103087656c033e972db8602a6f5cdc8","tid":45384,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇圖睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有係有 不過係屋企人 所以唔post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f6d40daefbc0f67687ae11ea8ad429d919c81a","tid":45384,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:27:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>色階我指既唔係色調<br />\n我指既係色彩過渡變化<br />\n<br />\n例如肉色去黑色RX100 可能過2000 種色咁，D750 係7-8000種左右</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係因為sensor大細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定唔同廠所以先咁</blockquote><br />\ncolor depth問題,sensor大d通常bit數都多D</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30adbe2cca3593bee7031d083e17d73c5cd65cc","tid":45384,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:27:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>sony white balance=垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n完全唔覺<br />\n係幾準<br />\n但室內日光過冷"},{"pid":"3e97aabcaff29dbf853f116b19b119582639d198","tid":45384,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:29:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\njpg 用住先就vivid -1 -1 +1<br />\nraw 就去mobile01 拎LR 改色調檔、上M9 AS<br />\n然後再用VSCO PRESET</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無知一問 點解要拎改色調檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSony本身無論jpg raw 影人都偏黃<br />\nm4開始有改善，m5紅色表現又再好一啲<br />\n但低光時效果仲係唔係好掂<br />\n<br />\n所以有啲人就抄咗其他機既調色、基本上一韃落去就可以換到，當然畫質係會有輕微既損失<br />\n<br />\n但至少你唔駛用個lightroom 調到屌那媽<br />\n當然有啲懶撚直接掟個VSCO PRESET就算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n部rx100低光都唔會旨意佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢都係陽光機來 只不過係好過dp1m啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38561a959946e531de7bbb30f0be4144c4f8e61b","tid":45384,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:37:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>sony white balance=垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n完全唔覺<br />\n係幾準<br />\n但室內日光過冷</blockquote><br />\n你拍片就明,室內白燈,大家都係5600,sony望落青bb,但canon完全冇事,最慘現場睇唔係青架"},{"pid":"82bd705352e56f5c05b761231e21267f64add202","tid":45384,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:41:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>sony white balance=垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n完全唔覺<br />\n係幾準<br />\n但室內日光過冷</blockquote><br />\n你拍片就明,室內白燈,大家都係5600,sony望落青bb,但canon完全冇事,最慘現場睇唔係青架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係Sony通病<br />\n因為佢個程式係預你好似Handy Cam咁用暖燈打燈<br />\n但老實講句，有Slog基本你想喺premiere點改都得啦"},{"pid":"efd602684dd39780c1865ecc91ce21bdcbbff9da","tid":45384,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:42:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>sony white balance=垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話事話，LR adjust white balance無Apple 個aperture咁准<br />\n平時aperture adjust white balance點落人塊面道就出到正確顏色<br />\nLR個WB一點落去成張相藍左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLR set WB真係要搵中灰位先得,點人面死硬<br />\n<br />\n同埋我發現adobe camera raw讀sony WB一定係高過機身睇到的WB值,次次都要手動set返準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家影人影風景都係用vsco 160 preset + vsco 160 camera calibration curve,唔同機個色彩都盡可能執返consistent"},{"pid":"e0bb5b7ba24e91f9600c731be017e0b35c72c832","tid":45384,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:43:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無知一問 點解要拎改色調檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSony本身無論jpg raw 影人都偏黃<br />\nm4開始有改善，m5紅色表現又再好一啲<br />\n但低光時效果仲係唔係好掂<br />\n<br />\n所以有啲人就抄咗其他機既調色、基本上一韃落去就可以換到，當然畫質係會有輕微既損失<br />\n<br />\n但至少你唔駛用個lightroom 調到屌那媽<br />\n當然有啲懶撚直接掟個VSCO PRESET就算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n部rx100低光都唔會旨意佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢都係陽光機來 只不過係好過dp1m啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得RX100 定位好明確，就係家庭機<br />\n帶小朋友一抽二lang時又想影靚相，又想自拍，又想部機靚仔，呢部機近乎係唯一選擇"},{"pid":"86196e77ff0d6aa3b61929f0b8bcb800640f85c2","tid":45384,"uid":1723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:44:22.000Z","msg":"RX100 質素真係好好，有時懶得拎多支kit鏡就拎多部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a1415ab1a7abd1a19e0ae0d4337bb3d5045cf0","tid":45384,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>sony white balance=垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話事話，LR adjust white balance無Apple 個aperture咁准<br />\n平時aperture adjust white balance點落人塊面道就出到正確顏色<br />\nLR個WB一點落去成張相藍左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLR set WB真係要搵中灰位先得,點人面死硬<br />\n<br />\n同埋我發現adobe camera raw讀sony WB一定係高過機身睇到的WB值,次次都要手動set返準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家影人影風景都係用vsco 160 preset + vsco 160 camera calibration curve,唔同機個色彩都盡可能執返consistent</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame我做法係<br />\nAdobe camera raw &gt; Leica M9 AS<br />\n微調後<br />\nVSCO NPC 160"},{"pid":"77091ace135b75b47550298e2b5cc160d0826be9","tid":45384,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:01:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>sony white balance=垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n完全唔覺<br />\n係幾準<br />\n但室內日光過冷</blockquote><br />\n你拍片就明,室內白燈,大家都係5600,sony望落青bb,但canon完全冇事,最慘現場睇唔係青架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我當初買來主要原因係拍片，d750 auto focus垃圾到狗都唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef599bc05e595beeb11393a666dd26996be6c5c","tid":45384,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:03:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>RX100 質素真係好好，有時懶得拎多支kit鏡就拎多部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開頭係買來拍片，心諗1&quot; sensor畫汁好打有限<br />\n點知有驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1041ddd3e977767ff8017ca61c094ead0081836","tid":45384,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:05:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話事話，LR adjust white balance無Apple 個aperture咁准<br />\n平時aperture adjust white balance點落人塊面道就出到正確顏色<br />\nLR個WB一點落去成張相藍左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLR set WB真係要搵中灰位先得,點人面死硬<br />\n<br />\n同埋我發現adobe camera raw讀sony WB一定係高過機身睇到的WB值,次次都要手動set返準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家影人影風景都係用vsco 160 preset + vsco 160 camera calibration curve,唔同機個色彩都盡可能執返consistent</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame我做法係<br />\nAdobe camera raw &amp;gt; Leica M9 AS<br />\n微調後<br />\nVSCO NPC 160</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAdobe camera raw同LR係兩樣野?<br />\nLR調WB好苦惱，又唔想aperture調完再import入LR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60da454e027b233230b30858166b5b516b9d49a6","tid":45384,"uid":9633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:05:48.000Z","msg":"Sony 直出差d"},{"pid":"9f6079a45daf60a410c3048e5f2b20002dff6d41","tid":45384,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:07:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sony 直出差d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n影開RAW檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講去到Mark V jpeg已經可以真出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecba55898ba437c246e1d6343b44583f81eef6e","tid":45384,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:09:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>sony white balance=垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n完全唔覺<br />\n係幾準<br />\n但室內日光過冷</blockquote><br />\n你拍片就明,室內白燈,大家都係5600,sony望落青bb,但canon完全冇事,最慘現場睇唔係青架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我當初買來主要原因係拍片，d750 auto focus垃圾到狗都唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拍片就唔用auto focus,本身sony鏡大部份都係 fly-by-wire,手動對焦勁難用,根本唔適合拍片,所以都係用canon鏡,但就會冇左拍片af"},{"pid":"90aa2f38bbeb38b04359eeeddb96f3710e7b8ef9","tid":45384,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:09:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話事話，LR adjust white balance無Apple 個aperture咁准<br />\n平時aperture adjust white balance點落人塊面道就出到正確顏色<br />\nLR個WB一點落去成張相藍左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLR set WB真係要搵中灰位先得,點人面死硬<br />\n<br />\n同埋我發現adobe camera raw讀sony WB一定係高過機身睇到的WB值,次次都要手動set返準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家影人影風景都係用vsco 160 preset + vsco 160 camera calibration curve,唔同機個色彩都盡可能執返consistent</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame我做法係<br />\nAdobe camera raw &amp;gt; Leica M9 AS<br />\n微調後<br />\nVSCO NPC 160</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAdobe camera raw同LR係兩樣野?<br />\nLR調WB好苦惱，又唔想aperture調完再import入LR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實camera raw係PS同LR讀入RAW的program<br />\n<br />\n我就算用左VSCO portra係室內都好易影人色黃,WB全部要manual點左中灰再減200-400K,但好易較到偏青色<br />\n<br />\n用d偏黃的鏡頭問題特別大,但用左VSCO已經有大幅改善"},{"pid":"7d9362756c2f34c9cb9e9195d27c3e7487272d86","tid":45384,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:14:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你拍片就明,室內白燈,大家都係5600,sony望落青bb,但canon完全冇事,最慘現場睇唔係青架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我當初買來主要原因係拍片，d750 auto focus垃圾到狗都唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拍片就唔用auto focus,本身sony鏡大部份都係 fly-by-wire,手動對焦勁難用,根本唔適合拍片,所以都係用canon鏡,但就會冇左拍片af</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n影BB仔點Manual focus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> rx100v 對焦真係好撚掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上FFsensor大淺景深仲易outfo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf68cb5a3febb1ef573961e33e8d95f93cf6dd3e","tid":45384,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:15:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame我做法係<br />\nAdobe camera raw &amp;amp;gt; Leica M9 AS<br />\n微調後<br />\nVSCO NPC 160</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAdobe camera raw同LR係兩樣野?<br />\nLR調WB好苦惱，又唔想aperture調完再import入LR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實camera raw係PS同LR讀入RAW的program<br />\n<br />\n我就算用左VSCO portra係室內都好易影人色黃,WB全部要manual點左中灰再減200-400K,但好易較到偏青色<br />\n<br />\n用d偏黃的鏡頭問題特別大,但用左VSCO已經有大幅改善</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁講啫入aperture set好WB再import入LR會好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45282fa8ee4dbd05f22e7bfea072f2c4ea12f5f","tid":45384,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:17:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你拍片就明,室內白燈,大家都係5600,sony望落青bb,但canon完全冇事,最慘現場睇唔係青架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我當初買來主要原因係拍片，d750 auto focus垃圾到狗都唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拍片就唔用auto focus,本身sony鏡大部份都係 fly-by-wire,手動對焦勁難用,根本唔適合拍片,所以都係用canon鏡,但就會冇左拍片af</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未必人人都要最專業嗰種既<br />\nvlog 黎講夠用"},{"pid":"933fa91bbbd1d6bf44afedd1ceb88683a1012871","tid":45384,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:21:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame我做法係<br />\nAdobe camera raw &amp;amp;gt; Leica M9 AS<br />\n微調後<br />\nVSCO NPC 160</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAdobe camera raw同LR係兩樣野?<br />\nLR調WB好苦惱，又唔想aperture調完再import入LR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實camera raw係PS同LR讀入RAW的program<