ormal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話事話，LR adjust white balance無Apple 個aperture咁准<br />\n平時aperture adjust white balance點落人塊面道就出到正確顏色<br />\nLR個WB一點落去成張相藍左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLR set WB真係要搵中灰位先得,點人面死硬<br />\n<br />\n同埋我發現adobe camera raw讀sony WB一定係高過機身睇到的WB值,次次都要手動set返準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家影人影風景都係用vsco 160 preset + vsco 160 camera calibration curve,唔同機個色彩都盡可能執返consistent</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame我做法係<br />\nAdobe camera raw &gt; Leica M9 AS<br />\n微調後<br />\nVSCO NPC 160</blockquote><br />\n邊隻160?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"668c3353917057b466e750d0d793b2a6bb9b0ede","tid":45384,"uid":45262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:49:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>sony white balance=垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話事話，LR adjust white balance無Apple 個aperture咁准<br />\n平時aperture adjust white balance點落人塊面道就出到正確顏色<br />\nLR個WB一點落去成張相藍左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLR set WB真係要搵中灰位先得,點人面死硬<br />\n<br />\n同埋我發現adobe camera raw讀sony WB一定係高過機身睇到的WB值,次次都要手動set返準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家影人影風景都係用vsco 160 preset + vsco 160 camera calibration curve,唔同機個色彩都盡可能執返consistent</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame我做法係<br />\nAdobe camera raw &gt; Leica M9 AS<br />\n微調後<br />\nVSCO NPC 160</blockquote><br />\n邊隻160?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nso - fuji 160定so-kodak portra 160?"},{"pid":"cd9722ce8ae6ae5b40ecb43a69f8c487f655c04f","tid":45384,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:51:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame我做法係<br />\nAdobe camera raw &amp;gt; Leica M9 AS<br />\n微調後<br />\nVSCO NPC 160</blockquote><br />\n邊隻160?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nso - fuji 160定so-kodak portra 160?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFuji啦梗係<br />\n不過自己調教下仲好<br />\nKodak嗰隻都好好用"},{"pid":"1271a3ec05b6c5a2d6c130d247baff811141a0b8","tid":45384,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:34:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n邊隻160?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nso - fuji 160定so-kodak portra 160?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFuji啦梗係<br />\n不過自己調教下仲好<br />\nKodak嗰隻都好好用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nVSCO d effect apply落人像道好重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3686297f2860a706d011915102ef0b216691c1","tid":45384,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nso - fuji 160定so-kodak portra 160?</blockquote><br />\n<